channel.title: LabJamz from THEMIXLAB.net
channel.description:
The Mix Lab Podcast presents "LabJamz" which brings you more on to the mixtape menu for those that enjoy other musical tastes. Listen online, download for free, hear it on your iPod, cruise with it in your ride, party to it, and subscribe or follow for more. At the LabJamz you'll hear DJ JFresh-One spinnin' jams like old school hip-hop, mixshow specials, mainstream hip-hop, R&B, soul, funk, slow jams, classic rock club/techno, reggaeton, radio hits, and remixes.
For more info or more podcasts check out... www.themixlab.net

item.title: LabJamz #20 - The Next Level: Summer Jam
item.description: Attention weekend warriors and party people! It's the JumpOff....start out the Summer of 2012 with Arizona's own, DJ JFresh-One as he delivers ANOTHER session to The Next Level series. This edition is simply known as Summer Jam. Enjoy a non-stop mix featuring the hot selections of Club, Dance, R&B, Top 40, Hip-Hop, remixes, and classics. >>>FOR MORE INFO & MIXTAPES: www.themixlab.net >>>JOIN US ON FACEBOOK: www.facebook.com/themixlab >>>FOLLOW US ON TWITTER: http://twitter.com/themixlab Tracklist: 01. item.title: LabJamz #19 - The Next Level (New Year 2012)
item.description: Welcome to The Next Level! It’s about that time to celebrate & bring in the new year! To start things off The Mix Lab & DJ JFresh-One would like to present to all of you this new Mixtape featuring party jams to help your celebration be a great one. Fresh mixes up a variety of tunes from today & the old school and a variety of tastes too. Majority is R&B, Top 40, Club, and Hip-Hop. So whether y’all having a house party, a big dance, club hopping, or need something to hype you up for the weekend….this is the mix for you! Enjoy, drive safe, and comeback for more jams! Happy 2012 everyone, God bless! Get at us on our website: www.themixlab.net Follow us on Twitter: http://twitter.com/themixlab Also join us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pages/TheMixLabnet/98413398331 On iTunes search: “The Mix Lab Podcast”

item.title: LabJamz #18 - Back To The Old School
item.description: WELCOME BACK! Yes, it's been quite a minute since a new episode was dropped on LabJamz! On this episode I got some MORE old school. Taking it back to the classics and mixin' it up! Here is some Hip-Hop, R&B, Rock, and Dance. I hope you all enjoyed the CruiseControl Series. I may drop in some more in or some more mixes & jams in the near future...keep a look out for more episodes. For more mixes or info on The Mix Lab hit up... www.themixlab.net Thank you, enjoy & God bless! -DJ JFresh-One http://jfreshone.webs.com http://twitter.com/themixlab

item.title: LabJamz #17 - CruiseControl 6
item.description: It's summertime peoples and here some music to get your weekend started! Welcome back to THEMIXLAB's own "LabJamz"...your hook-up to remixes, club hits, today's bangers, and old school flashbacks! Here on this mix is an addition to the CruiseControl Series. This is CruiseControl 6.0 and its all put together by DJ JFresh-One of THEMIXLAB. This type of mix is intended for those party heads or weekend warriors. So this will contain radio friendly urban hits along with a splash of old school. Tune in, Listen, Subscribe, and download a copy....FOR FREE! Stay update & follow us on Twitter.com/themixlab You want some REAL dope hip-hop? Check out www.themixlab.net
